languages.text: "Ты знаешь, кто говорит. Ты знаешь, что я рядом и не оставлю тебя в покое. Наслаждайся украденной у меня властью, пока можешь. Но я с тобой еще не закончил!"
"You know who this is. You know I'm close and will never leave you be. Enjoy the power you stole from me while you can. But I'm not done with you yet!"

languages.text: 「久しぶりだな。私は常にお前の近くにいて、決してお前から離れない…お前もそれを知っているはずだ。私から奪った力を今のうちに存分に楽しむといい。だが、絶対に貴様は逃さぬ！」
languages.original_text: "You know who this is. You know I'm close and will never leave you be. Enjoy the power you stole from me while you can. But I'm not done with you yet!"

languages.text: “你知道我是谁，你知道我就在你身边，永远不会离开你。尽情享受你从我这里偷走的力量吧，但我和你还没完！”
languages.original_text: "You know who this is. You know I'm close and will never leave you be. Enjoy the power you stole from me while you can. But I'm not done with you yet!"

languages.text: «Ya sabes quién soy. Sabes que estoy cerca y que nunca te dejaré en paz. Disfruta del poder que me has robado mientras puedas, ¡pero no he terminado contigo!».
languages.original_text: "You know who this is. You know I'm close and will never leave you be. Enjoy the power you stole from me while you can. But I'm not done with you yet!"

languages.text: « Vous savez qui je suis. Vous savez que je suis tout proche et que je ne vous laisserai jamais tranquille. Savourez le pouvoir que vous m'avez volé tant que vous le pouvez, mais je n'en ai pas encore fini avec vous ! »
languages.original_text: "You know who this is. You know I'm close and will never leave you be. Enjoy the power you stole from me while you can. But I'm not done with you yet!"

languages.text: "Ihr wisst, wer ich bin. Ihr wisst, ich bin in der Nähe und werde Euch niemals in Ruhe lassen. Genießt die Macht, die Ihr mir gestohlen habt, solange Ihr könnt. Aber ich bin noch nicht fertig mit Euch!"
languages.original_text: "You know who this is. You know I'm close and will never leave you be. Enjoy the power you stole from me while you can. But I'm not done with you yet!"

languages.text: "Benim kim olduğumu biliyorsun. Yakında olduğumu ve peşini asla bırakmayacağımı biliyorsun. Benden çaldığın gücün fırsatın varken tadını çıkar. Seninle daha işim bitmedi!"
